I"¯<p>A posthuman is an <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/transhuman-singularity-is-driven-by-cognitive-enhancement">individual</a> so radically <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/second-brain-architecture-guides-cognitive-augmentation">augmented</a> by means of <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/tools-for-thought-should-amplify-fundamental-capabilities">technology</a> that granting them human status is no longer trivial. In this context, transhumanism is the liminal phase between human and posthuman, characterized by <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/transhuman-singularity-is-driven-by-cognitive-enhancement">a technological explosion</a>.</p>
